Live com a @itsnunaa para falar sobre racismo, racismo sistemático, o que podes fazer para ajudar, etc

Obrigada Nuna pelas tuas palavras e sabedoria, e por teres tirado este tempo para falar comigo! 
Live with @itsnunaa about racism, sistematic racism, what you can do to help, and much more! 
Thank you Nuna for taking the time to talk to me! You are so amazing, and you have an incredible voice!

node.text: We are all in!!!! @jastookes @josephineskriver @laisribeiro  and myself have accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE. Go to the link in bio and watch this video to see what we have planed for you and a guest! We cant wait to meet you and take you on the most awesome day in LA. Let’s all make a positive impact during this very difficult time. We challenge @zedd, @zendaya, and @zacefron to go ALL IN! Donations benefit @nokidhungry, @mealsonwheelsamerica and #americasfoodfund which benefits @feedingamerica and @wckitchen
